    static  checkIfRegulationAreComplied = (data) => {

        if (!data.regulation) return false 
        if (
            (data.stateInput=== data.regulation.state) &&
            (data.personAmountInput<=data.regulation.maxPersonsClosedRooms )

            console.log("Genehmigt")
            return true
        } else{
            console.log("nicht Genehmigt")
            return false
        }
